== Over view ==
Forum tool aims to solve all the needs you want to use in a forum. It use firefox as a platform.

It will provide the service as list bellow.
 * Change login on the fly.
 * Track the post you want.
 * Single place to post multiple posts.
 * Manage all your posts in multiple site in one place.

Now the version of forum tool is 0.1, it only supports change login on the fly.


